<%- include('../template/_header', {
    meta: {
        title: '店舗情報・スタッフ紹介',
        description: 'サロンのコンセプト、スタッフ紹介、店内写真、アクセス情報をご案内します',
        siteType: 'website',
        url: 'about/',
    }
}) %>
<div id="page-transition-overlay" class="page-transition-overlay"></div>
<main class="salonMain salonMain_type_about">
    <section class="salonAboutHero">
        <div class="salonAboutHero__visual">
            <div class="salonAboutHero__imageWrapper">
                <img class="salonAboutHero__image" src="/images/salon/hero_about.png" alt="About Us" loading="eager" />
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="salonAboutHero__content">
            <div class="salonAboutHero__textWrapper">
                <h1 class="salonAboutHero__title">
                    <span class="salonAboutHero__revealText"><span>About</span></span>
                    <span class="salonAboutHero__revealText"><span>Us</span></span>
                </h1>
                <p class="salonAboutHero__subtitle fadein delay-200">
                    美意識と静寂が<br>交差する場所
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="salonAboutConcept">
        <div class="salonAboutConcept__bgText">Concept</div>
        <div class="salonAboutConcept__inner">
            <div class="salonAboutConcept__header fadein">
                <h2 class="salonAboutConcept__title uiHeading uiHeading_level_h2">Concept</h2>
                <p class="salonAboutConcept__lead">
                    余白を楽しみ、<br>
                    本質を見つめる。
                </p>
            </div>
            <div class="salonAboutConcept__content fadein delay-200">
                <p class="salonAboutConcept__text">
                    私たちは、ヘアデザインを通じて<br>
                    お客様の「在り方」を表現します。<br>
                    装飾的であることよりも、<br>
                    内側から溢れ出る美しさを大切にしています。
                </p>
                <div class="salonAboutConcept__features">
                    <div class="salonAboutConcept__feature">
                        <span class="salonAboutConcept__number">01</span>
                        <h3 class="salonAboutConcept__subtitle">Counseling</h3>
                        <p class="salonAboutConcept__desc">言葉にならない「なりたい」を汲み取る。</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="salonAboutConcept__feature">
                        <span class="salonAboutConcept__number">02</span>
                        <h3 class="salonAboutConcept__subtitle">Space</h3>
                        <p class="salonAboutConcept__desc">五感を解き放つ、ミニマルな空間。</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="salonAboutConcept__feature">
                        <span class="salonAboutConcept__number">03</span>
                        <h3 class="salonAboutConcept__subtitle">Technique</h3>
                        <p class="salonAboutConcept__desc">骨格を美しく魅せる、建築的なカット。</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="salonStaff">
        <div class="salonStaff__inner">
            <div class="salonStaff__header fadein">
                <h2 class="salonStaff__title uiHeading uiHeading_level_h2">Staff</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="salonStaff__list">
                <div class="salonStaff__item fadein">
                    <div class="salonStaff__image">
                        <img class="salonStaff__imageImg" src="/images/salon/about/staff_01.jpg" alt="Sakura Tanaka" loading="lazy" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="salonStaff__content">
                        <p class="salonStaff__position">Top Stylist</p>
                        <h3 class="salonStaff__name">Sakura Tanaka</h3>
                        <p class="salonStaff__comment">毎日のスタイリングが楽しくなるような、再現性の高いカットを心がけています。</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="salonStaff__item fadein delay-100">
                    <div class="salonStaff__image">
                        <img class="salonStaff__imageImg" src="/images/salon/about/staff_02.jpg" alt="Yuki Sato" loading="lazy" />
                    </div>
                    <div class="salonStaff__content">
                        <p class="salonStaff__position">Colorist</p>
                        <h3 class="salonStaff__name">Yuki Sato</h3>
                        <p class="salonStaff__comment">透明感のあるカラーや、デザインカラーもお任せください。</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="salonGallery">
        <div class="salonGallery__inner">
            <div class="salonGallery__header fadein">
                <h2 class="salonGallery__title uiHeading uiHeading_level_h2">Gallery</h2>
            </div>
            <div class="salonGallery__grid">
                <div class="salonGallery__item fadein">
                    <figure class="salonGallery__figure">
                        <img class="salonGallery__image" src="/images/salon/interior_1.png" alt="Main Floor" loading="lazy" />
                        <figcaption class="salonGallery__caption">Main Floor</figcaption>
                    </figure>
                </div>
                <div class="salonGallery__item fadein delay-100">
                    <figure class="salonGallery__figure">
                        <img class="salonGallery__image" src="https://picsum.photos/800/1000?random=201" alt="Shampoo Booth" loading="lazy" />
                        <figcaption class="salonGallery__caption">Shampoo Booth</figcaption>
                    </figure>
                </div>
                <div class="salonGallery__item fadein delay-200">
                    <figure class="salonGallery__figure">
                        <img class="salonGallery__image" src="https://picsum.photos/1000/800?random=202" alt="Waiting Area" loading="lazy" />
                        <figcaption class="salonGallery__caption">Waiting Area</figcaption>
                    </figure>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="salonInfo">
        <div class="salonInfo__inner">
            <h2 class="salonInfo__title uiHeading uiHeading_level_h2 fadein">Information</h2>
            <dl class="salonInfo__list fadein delay-200">
                <div class="salonInfo__item">
                    <dt class="salonInfo__dt">Salon Name</dt>
                    <dd class="salonInfo__dd"><%= typeof config !== 'undefined' && config.salon && config.salon.name ? config.salon.name : 'Lumière Salon' %></dd>
                </div>
                <div class="salonInfo__item">
                    <dt class="salonInfo__dt">Address</dt>
                    <dd class="salonInfo__dd"><%- typeof config !== 'undefined' && config.salon && config.salon.address ? config.salon.address.replace(/ /g, '<br>') : '〒107-0062<br>東京都港区南青山3-1-1' %></dd>
                </div>
                <div class="salonInfo__item">
                    <dt class="salonInfo__dt">Tel</dt>
                    <dd class="salonInfo__dd">
                        <a class="salonInfo__link" href="tel:03-1234-5678">03-1234-5678</a>
                    </dd>
                </div>
                <div class="salonInfo__item">
                    <dt class="salonInfo__dt">Open</dt>
                    <dd class="salonInfo__dd">10:00 - 20:00</dd>
                </div>
                <div class="salonInfo__item">
                    <dt class="salonInfo__dt">Close</dt>
                    <dd class="salonInfo__dd">Tuesday</dd>
                </div>
                <div class="salonInfo__item">
                    <dt class="salonInfo__dt">Payment</dt>
                    <dd class="salonInfo__dd">Cash, Credit Card, QR Payment</dd>
                </div>
            </dl>
        </div>
    </section>

    <section class="salonAccess" id="access">
        <div class="salonAccess__inner">
            <h2 class="salonAccess__title uiHeading uiHeading_level_h2 fadein">Access</h2>
            <div class="salonAccess__content fadein delay-200">
                <div class="salonAccess__map">
                    <iframe class="salonAccess__mapIframe" src="https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3241.747975468372!2d139.74324421525823!3d35.65858048019498!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x60188b9a6b8c1e6d%3A0x1c3e3b3b3b3b3b3b!2z44CSMTAwLTAwMDAg5p2x5Lqs6YO95riL6LC35Yy65p2x5Lqs77yR5LiB55uu77yV4oiS77yW!5e0!3m2!1sja!2sjp!4v1234567890123!5m2!1sja!2sjp" width="100%" height="450" style="border:0;" allowfullscreen="" loading="lazy" referrerpolicy="no-referrer-when-downgrade"></iframe>
                </div>
                <div class="salonAccess__info">
                    <dl class="salonAccess__infoItem">
                        <dt class="salonAccess__infoDt">Station</dt>
                        <dd class="salonAccess__infoDd">Omotesando Sta. 5min walk</dd>
                    </dl>
                    <div class="salonAccess__route">
                        <h3 class="salonAccess__routeTitle">Route</h3>
                        <ol class="salonAccess__routeList">
                            <li class="salonAccess__routeItem">表参道駅 A4出口を出て左へ</li>
                            <li class="salonAccess__routeItem">最初の交差点を右折</li>
                            <li class="salonAccess__routeItem">突き当たりを左折してすぐ</li>
                        </ol>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
</main>
<%- include('../template/_footer', {
    scripts: []
}) %>

